public abstract void addCustomHistory(long guid,
                                      String historyMessage)
all the modifications (eg. addition/deletion of attachment, user annotation, visual annotation, comments, record creation) are implicitly added as history to every record by the server. THIS METHOD NEED NOT BE USED FOR SUCH MODIFICATIONS. The purpose of this method is to add any special custom history message to the record.
